snippet.title: Rumbleverse | Season Two Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Rumbleverse Season Two is live! The bridge is open, and the champions of Grapital City are battling it out at the all-new sunny sites of Low Key Key. Download this Brawler Royale for free and launch into the rumble on vacation @PlayStation, @Xbox, and PC via the @Epic Games store. 

Website: https://www.rumbleverse.com 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/rumbleverse 
Support: https://twitter.com/RumbleSupport 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/rumbleverse 
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@rumbleverse 
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/rumbleverse 
Discord: https://www.discord.gg/rumbleverse 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rumbleverse
